The [[science fiction]] [[novel]] '''''Ca<U+0142>a prawda o planecie Ksi''''' ([[1983]]) (''The Complete Truth about planet Xi'') by [[Janusz A. Zajdel]] is about a far off colony which had become something similar to both [[kolkhoz]] and a labour camp.  The colony is visited by the inspectors arriving in secret to discover why they do not answer any messages from the Earth.

